#MEM id=rules source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/dev/skills/design-and-build/vercel-react-best-practices/rules/bundle-defer-third-party.md
M|rules|title: Defer Non-Critical Third-Party Libraries
M|rules|impact: MEDIUM
M|rules|impactDescription: loads after hydration
M|rules|tags: bundle, third-party, anl, defer
M|rules|anl, logging, and error tracking don't block user interaction. Load them after hydration.
M|rules|**Incorrect (blocks initial bundle):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import { anl } from '@vercel/anl/react'
M|rules|export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<html>
M|rules|<body>
M|rules|{children}
M|rules|<anl />
M|rules|</body>
M|rules|</html>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|**Correct (loads after hydration):**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import dynamic from 'next/dynamic'
M|rules|const anl = dynamic(
M|rules|() => import('@vercel/anl/react').then(m => m.anl),
M|rules|{ ssr: false }
M|rules|)
M|rules|export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<html>
M|rules|<body>
M|rules|{children}
M|rules|<anl />
M|rules|</body>
M|rules|</html>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```